August, 1983

It's 9pm on a Friday night. You are seated at a DESK on which sits a home COMPUTER. A DESK LAMP provides the room's only illumination. A GAME BOX is on the desk.

Try looking around the room for a bit. For example, type LOOK AT COMPUTER or simply LOOK COMPUTER. If you lose track of what objects are in the room, just say LOOK.

Type DONE LOOKING or DONE when you're finished.

