> look at game box

'Quest for the Serpent's Eye: A Text-Based Jungle Adventure Game' is written on the front of the box, along with 'Exclusive Hint Book and glow-in-the-dark Compass Included!' in the bottom corner.

It has taken you two months' worth of mowing lawns to get to this moment. Your spine tingles with excitement at the thought of the hours of entertainment that await you.

