Game Manual for
Quest for the Serpent’s Eye

Welcome to the Island of Ankrum!

Quest for the Serpent’s Eye is a text-based graphic adventure game where YOU are the hero. You will make every choice, overcome every obstacle, and be expected to solve every puzzle to reach your goal.

Every step brings you closer to your goal, but be warned: danger lurks around every corner!

So grab your walking stick and compass - your greatest adventure awaits!

Type NEXT PAGE to continue reading or CLOSE MANUAL to return to the game.
