Welcome to the Island of Ankrum! You are standing on a weathered wooden dock. You can see the rusted hulk of a steamship that brought you to this island sailing off in the distance. For better or worse, you're stuck here.

The GAME MANUAL is sitting on the dock. The island's only VILLAGE is to the NORTH. The OCEAN is to the SOUTH.

Type GO NORTH, or simply N.
