Without the faint breeze it's even warmer in the trading post than outside. Flies buzz around your head.

The SHOPKEEPER stands in the shade. A SIGN hangs on the nearby wall.

"Take a look at my fine merchandise! Better take everything you can if you're headed into the jungle. It's so cheap it's practically free! If you need more info just ASK. Name's Stan, by the way."

Go WEST to return to the village square.
