Now might be a good time to record your progress. You can do this at any time by typing SAVE into the command bar. You'd better make absolutely certain that you're carrying everything you think you'll need to complete your quest. We can't guarantee you'll be able to retreat SOUTH to the safety of the village for long...

Head NORTH when you're ready to begin your quest!
