> w

As you crawl through the tunnel you start to hear a low rumbling from above, followed by a cloud of fine rock dust.
You tumble into a larger cavern just in time to see the tunnel collapse behind you - and cut off all remaining light.

It would appear that you're totally Zorked. I guess you'll have to feel your way from here.
