> knock five times

> knock five times

You knock five times. Professor P answers the door within seconds. Upon seeing your disheveled state he chuckles and shakes his head before flashing a knowing smile. "Did you find what you were looking for, my friend?"

Without giving it much thought, you shake your head, hand the amulet back to him, and say nothing more on the subject.

Press any key to continue.

"That's probably for the best," he replies. "Sometimes it is better to let myths continue to be just that - myths."

He pats your shoulder. "I'm afraid I'll have to cut our meeting short. I'm in the midst of a rather heated chess game..." and shuts the door.

Press any key to continue.

You stand on the stern deck of the ship staring longingly back at the Island of Ankrum as it fades into the distance, and ponder which version of your tale you’ll tell your colleagues upon your return. Fortunately you have many weeks of sea travel ahead of you in which to decide.

THE END

